{"tid":538230,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"一人一個最頂唔順既煩膠同學","createTime":"2018-01-23T12:27:43.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-23T12:27:43.000Z","uid":126397,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"ff7234aac820e1922aec095e491a0a150a16ebdf","tid":538230,"uid":126397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-23T12:27:43.000Z","msg":"開左學半年，<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 都仲係頂唔順我啲煩膠同學<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 諗住對耐啲習慣左會好啲，但係佢真係好煩，又自大又成日狗眼看人低，<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 明明佢成績又唔係好過我，同佢同組做group project先頂唔到，成個project都好似佢主導哂咁樣，成日ban其他人既idea，但係ban人純粹係佢自己唔中意，佢自己又俾唔到suggestion，<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 最後咪又係我同個friend做哂成份project。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有冇巴絲都有遇到呢啲煩膠。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}